OpenLearning,is,an,educational,platform,for,social,learning,Users,can,sign,up,for,any,course,they,would,like,for,free,They,can,also,sign,up,in,groups,and,take,courses,socially,Educators,can,create,their,courses,as,well,to,share,with,the,world,at,large,The,OpenLearning,API,exposes,the,system,of,notifications,about,course,usage,and,user,activity,It,is,a,RESTful,API,that,returns,JSON,encoded,data,It,can,be,used,for,integrating,of,OpenLearning,into,scripts